-- Oracle offers to buy BEA Systems for $6.66 billion
-- 
-- Fri Oct 12, 2007 7:14am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/12/us-beasystes-oracle-idUSWNAS619220071012

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Oracle Corp ORCL.O on Friday said it offered to buy BEA Systems Inc BEAS.O for about $6.66 billion to help strengthen its position in the commercial software market. 

 Oracle offered $17 per share in cash for BEA, which is a 25 percent premium over BEA's closing stock price on Thursday. (Reporting by  Bill Berkrot )